        IBMECMSearchTemplateBuilder select(String[] columns,
                                   String sortBy,
                                   boolean sortAscending,
                                   int pageSize)
        Sets columns to be displayed in the search result. If any of these settings is nil, the default value will be set.
        Parameters:
        columns - the columns to be displayed in the search results
        sortBy - the sort column
        sortAscending - true to sort in ascending order
        pageSize - the page size of the search results
        Returns:
        a reference to IBMECMSearchTemplateBuilder

      • from

        IBMECMSearchTemplateBuilder from(String[] classes,
                                 boolean includeSubClasses,
                                 IBMECMObjectType objectType)
        Setd the classes to be searched on.
        Parameters:
        classes - the classes to be searched on. If not set, the base class based on object type is used
        includeSubClasses - true to include subclasses
        objectType - the type of object you must specify to search for. See IBMECMObjectType for a list of types
        Returns:
        a reference to IBMECMSearchTemplateBuilder

      • where

        IBMECMSearchTemplateBuilder where(IBMECMSearchPredicate[] searchPredicates,
                                  IBMECMSearchPredicatesRelation relation)
        Sets the search criterials for properties. The relation between search criteria for properties and text search criteria is always conjuction (intersection).
        Parameters:
        searchPredicates - the predicates to be used as search criteria
        relation - the relation among these predicates
        Returns:
        a reference to IBMECMSearchTemplateBuilder
